{
  "npc_id": "lin",
  "greetings": [
    {
      "id": "lin_greet_morning",
      "text": "早啊，$[PLAYER_NAME]。老头子我起得早，习惯了。你也起得早，不错。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "清晨",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_greet_afternoon",
      "text": "午后了，$[PLAYER_NAME]。老头子刚晒了会儿太阳，你这会儿过来有事？",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "午后",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_greet_evening",
      "text": "傍晚了，$[PLAYER_NAME]。一天的活儿都干完了吧？进来坐坐。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "傍晚",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_greet_night",
      "text": "这么晚还不睡啊，$[PLAYER_NAME]。老头子我也就这时候能安静坐一会儿。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "夜晚",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_greet_spring",
      "text": "春天来了，$[PLAYER_NAME]。老头子这老骨头最盼的就是春天了。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "春",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_greet_summer",
      "text": "夏天热啊，$[PLAYER_NAME]。年轻的时候我不怕热，现在可不行了。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "夏",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_greet_autumn",
      "text": "秋天啊，是老头子最喜欢的季节。$[PLAYER_NAME]，你知道为什么吗？",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "秋",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_greet_winter",
      "text": "冬天冷，$[PLAYER_NAME]。老头子给你烧壶热茶暖暖身子。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "冬",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_greet_mist",
      "text": "薄雾天啊，$[PLAYER_NAME]。我这老寒腿比什么天气预报都准。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "薄雾",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_greet_tide",
      "text": "大潮来了，$[PLAYER_NAME]。以前在海上跑船的时候，最盼就是这种日子。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "大潮",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_greet_high",
      "text": "……$[PLAYER_NAME]，看到你啊，老头子就想起自己的孩子。",
      "favor_min": 200,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 6,
      "heart_max": 10
    }
  ],
  "small_talks": [
    {
      "id": "lin_st_sea_1",
      "text": "我在海上跑了大半辈子，$[PLAYER_NAME]。后来年纪大了，就来这儿给老朋友看家。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_st_sea_2",
      "text": "大海是有脾气的，$[PLAYER_NAME]。你要是和它对着干，它就把你吞了。但你顺着它，它就送你回家。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_st_weather",
      "text": "今天的$[WEATHER]……看云海就知道明天什么天。海上那套，这儿也用得上。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_st_cloud",
      "text": "云海和海浪是一样的，$[PLAYER_NAME]。你看那云浪，一波一波的，有节奏。懂了这个，就懂了这片山。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_st_heart_low",
      "text": "$[PLAYER_NAME]，你这孩子不错，在这山庄住着，有心就能扎下根。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 100,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_st_heart_mid",
      "text": "外公那孩子走得早……$[PLAYER_NAME]，他把你托付给我照顾。现在看来，是他照顾我才对。",
      "favor_min": 50,
      "favor_max": 400,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 2,
      "heart_max": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_st_heart_high",
      "text": "$[PLAYER_NAME]，我这老头子这辈子没什么出息，但能遇到你们这些人，值了。",
      "favor_min": 200,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 6,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_st_dock",
      "text": "码头那边风大，$[PLAYER_NAME]。以前我总在那儿修船，现在老了，爬不动了。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    }
  ],
  "farewells": [
    {
      "id": "lin_farewell_1",
      "text": "去吧，$[PLAYER_NAME]。老头子还要在这儿坐会儿。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_farewell_2",
      "text": "慢点走，别摔了。$[PLAYER_NAME]，明天见。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_farewell_3",
      "text": "去吧。有空来坐坐，老头子这儿茶水管够。$[PLAYER_NAME]。",
      "favor_min": 50,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 3,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "lin_farewell_high",
      "text": "早点休息，$[PLAYER_NAME]。明天……我们再聊。",
      "favor_min": 200,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
